15:7](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#007.md), Asa succeeds him; [Kg1
15:9](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#009.md), Asa's good reign; [Kg1
15:16](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#016.md), The war between Baasha and him
