15:23](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#023.md), Jehoshaphat succeeds Asa; [Kg1
15:25](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#025.md), Nadab's wicked reign; [Kg1
15:27](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#027.md), Baasha conspiring against him,
executes Ahijah's prophecy; [Kg1
15:31](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#031.md), Nadab's acts and death; [Kg1
15:33](../../../bib/kjv/kg1015.htm#033.md), Baasha's wicked reign.

